sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Embed as Embedding Provider<br/>(vLLM / sentence-transformers)
    participant VecDB as Vector Store<br/>(Milvus/pgvector/Qdrant)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Client Inference Request
        Client->>LS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (no auth)
        LS->>vLLM: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP<br/>Auth: API token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
        vLLM-->>LS: LLM response
        LS->>PG: Log inference<br/>PostgreSQL 5432/TCP<br/>Auth: username/password
        LS-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,VecDB: Flow 2: RAG Pipeline (Vector Search + Inference)
        Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents/* or /v1/vector-io/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (no auth)
        LS->>Embed: Generate embeddings<br/>HTTP (configurable port)<br/>Auth: API token
        Embed-->>LS: Embedding vectors
        LS->>VecDB: Vector similarity search<br/>gRPC/HTTP/PostgreSQL (configurable)<br/>Auth: API key/password
        VecDB-->>LS: Relevant documents
        LS->>vLLM: Inference with context<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000/TCP<br/>Auth: API token
        vLLM-->>LS: Augmented response
        LS-->>Client: RAG response<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Evaluation Job (Remote RAGAS/Garak via Kubeflow)
        Client->>LS: POST /v1/eval/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (no auth)
        LS->>KFP: Submit evaluation pipeline<br/>HTTPS (configurable)<br/>Auth: API token (KUBEFLOW_PIPELINES_TOKEN)
        KFP->>S3: Store evaluation artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
        S3-->>KFP: Confirmation
        KFP-->>LS: Pipeline result
        LS-->>Client: Evaluation results<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    end
